{"tid":42411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集腋成裘]儲水式熱水爐使用攻略","createTime":"2016-12-16T15:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T10:49:12.000Z","uid":32762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4682d5651793d003425b5ef26a9b745a3cf783b2","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"又凍喇 各位用緊儲水式熱水爐嘅巴打有冇心得可以令沖涼好過啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我嗰個爐硬件上經多年改良 而家已經好好多<br />\n<br />\n基本設備: 18L儲水式熱水爐 <br />\n<br />\n建議配備: <br />\n<br />\n1.) 慳水花灑頭 (節水量30%起跳)<br />\n<br />\n2.) 可方便快捷調整合適溫度嘅水龍頭 否則經常一開水灼熟自己或凍到心臟病發 更浪費大量熱水同時間去調節溫度 <br />\n(以前用嗰個係六角型偏圓型嘅水龍頭 搽完梘要行去洗手盆沖淨隻手先扭開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日凍到震住咁行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要分開冷熱兩個制 成日扭得太實開得一邊開唔到另一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 思考左好耐到底應該開邊邊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好在而家換番一條柄向左凍向右熱嗰種)<br />\n<br />\n一冬天真係沖涼都要度個rundown 要一開始唔可以太熱 每次搽梘、洗臉、洗頭都要迫自己熄水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熄水前先可以歎幾秒熱啲嘅水嚟確保熄水後冇咁快凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲成日要諗點樣group埋一齊過水 eg 洗頭洗臉一次過過水 之後護髮素同沖涼液一齊過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現水龍頭扭到最熱都淨係出微暖水嗰一刻 簡直好似判刑一樣 個爐喺度恥笑你計錯數沖唔切涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時消極起上嚟 真係要等日頭最暖嗰刻先敢沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add72ed4d9983fab1cfad7662a19e507ec962f79","tid":42411,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"洗完第一轉水果時個口含定啲水<br />\n凍果陣吐出黎<br />\n即刻暖返曬"},{"pid":"705819bbd49c9a45b33e9cdb7eeda0b27b29cf83","tid":42411,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"一個字，快，我個陣5分鐘沖完"},{"pid":"071e1bcef6a754d319fc3a2352240d48606017ff","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個字，快，我個陣5分鐘沖完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快哂都要15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924453a243f313d51d530a8710aa958645f57886","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗完第一轉水果時個口含定啲水<br />\n凍果陣吐出黎<br />\n即刻暖返曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口容量要極大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722fe0580a4421d862cf7f51b053963a5dc7a4a8","tid":42411,"uid":52360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"洗頭/洗臉嗰陣，用條毛巾濕熱水搭係背脊，熄水嗰陣無咁易凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n［原始jj］有時搵個桶載定熱水，要全熱，因為要等熱水爐再煲水，再等佢煲好，就有多一桶用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f92801c1ea472b7389d710fa13a8c0f13836ad5","tid":42411,"uid":15030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:33:03.000Z","msg":"用咗好多年<br />\n贈你四個字: 唯快不破<br />\n利申: 5分鐘搞掂"},{"pid":"af2a64454c438dc3f9502e1e5df5eb5cb6460168","tid":42411,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗頭/洗臉嗰陣，用條毛巾濕熱水搭係背脊，熄水嗰陣無咁易凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n［原始jj］有時搵個桶載定熱水，要全熱，因為要等熱水爐再煲水，再等佢煲好，就有多一桶用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會裝多桶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n可以用桶水洗頭先順便等第二煲水滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b475e3457b17894ba51b98ef78063849da771fb3","tid":42411,"uid":63687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗頭/洗臉嗰陣，用條毛巾濕熱水搭係背脊，熄水嗰陣無咁易凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n［原始jj］有時搵個桶載定熱水，要全熱，因為要等熱水爐再煲水，再等佢煲好，就有多一桶用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會裝多桶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n可以用桶水洗頭先順便等第二煲水滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都係用儲水式<br />\n但係唔知點解覺得你地好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb39acbabd289d3730ada5dff51588e90311494","tid":42411,"uid":9298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:10:59.000Z","msg":"1. 贏在起跑線比一切都重要，儲水式熱水爐最重要果三隻字： 儲水，容量越大越，享受時間越長，有位最好換中央儲水式，慳住水用沖廿分鐘不是夢<br />\n<br />\n2. 收放自如，用儲水式熱水爐一定要同部爐做到人爐合一，熱水一定唔可以全出，要細水長流等部爐有少少時間可以回氣煲返熱d 新水"},{"pid":"970752dbbdc36a6667b35a6467cc77dd9da61360","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T22:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗頭/洗臉嗰陣，用條毛巾濕熱水搭係背脊，熄水嗰陣無咁易凍死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n［原始jj］有時搵個桶載定熱水，要全熱，因為要等熱水爐再煲水，再等佢煲好，就有多一桶用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會裝多桶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n可以用桶水洗頭先順便等第二煲水滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都係用儲水式<br />\n但係唔知點解覺得你地好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起細個連熱水爐都冇 都係裝桶水嚟沖"},{"pid":"30ed512854b764fed49d4fef769da9df4a196e21","tid":42411,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T23:01:18.000Z","msg":"一睇你話18L就知你基本野都錯撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾大買幾大，家陣屋企隻野係30L"},{"pid":"6911dde8d4ff8a66649fdd4e809cb21fee395c6c","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一睇你話18L就知你基本野都錯撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾大買幾大，家陣屋企隻野係30L</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水電佬話我屋企啲電系統太舊 support唔到30L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關唔關事？係咪俾人呃左？"},{"pid":"6ab4a82a6c5b7468a92579cf041e3e4182ffd6e0","tid":42411,"uid":10317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"諗返起晒以前用儲水式既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656e3fc77fece89510616aeccbb4ac2dd5b3146b","tid":42411,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:09:05.000Z","msg":"外部設備一定係閂門閂窗<br />\n抽氣扇都一定要熄<br />\n盡量保持沖涼既蒸氣留係入面<br />\n從而保持高溫度<br />\n咁搽身洗頭就無咁凍<br />\n<br />\n利申: 過來人"},{"pid":"234f0b7f67322917ae8ffed50b1fee850db0c9f1","tid":42411,"uid":52352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:11:08.000Z","msg":"由細用到大，以前用過一款得五六分鐘熱水嘅爐，不過好快壞左，之後基本上三四年唔夠就換一個，黎到依家用緊熱水爐夠沖十五分鐘，不過唔可以開得太大水同太熱，如果唔係要用幻想力將最後沖身時間嘅凍水當作熱水，唔係凍到震係熱到跳舞"},{"pid":"06840cfefec47bf252b382aad4d6d9f8041a968f","tid":42411,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:11:16.000Z","msg":"十分鐘  洗頭洗臉沖涼<br />\n岩岩好用哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係18L"},{"pid":"f0fb7172d699605f44ab5c21a7d5ef4da4bc533d","tid":42411,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:13:40.000Z","msg":"速度 屋企個爐天氣凍得三分鐘貨 就用呢三分鐘爆發小宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fbcdd91045a8acd297cd05e12cbcb5778511da","tid":42411,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:14:04.000Z","msg":"怕咩 天氣愈凍 用家就愈強大<br />\n利申 用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8526afd4b1491083b45d42b67bdca35fd37ea6a4","tid":42411,"uid":40255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:18:56.000Z","msg":"攻略一<br />\n著住衫洗頭洗面先/ 分開洗頭<br />\n<br />\n攻略二<br />\n如果係冷熱出水<br />\n熱水果面出小小<br />\n多啲凍水<br />\n啲水凍就較返小啲凍水<br />\n唔得先出返多啲熱水<br />\n<br />\n攻略三<br />\n用慳水花灑<br />\n<br />\n攻略四<br />\n有巴打講<br />\n天下武功為快不破<br />\n只要比個爐更快搞掂佢點都攻你唔入<br />\n<br />\n攻略五<br />\n踩住個盤沖<br />\n等啲熱水浸住隻腳<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n車房用儲水式熱水爐<br />\n無熱水快過超人"},{"pid":"50ee38eb3a286932819748db4b8c42d36baebef5","tid":42411,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T00:27:39.000Z","msg":"點解要用儲水式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a80f7870f0dbaf60b321ad1363011ba43ffdca7","tid":42411,"uid":52360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要用儲水式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有頭髮邊個想做癩痢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ee74e253b71c332bacefd8a4ed650aa02a2c75","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗返起晒以前用儲水式既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好羨慕巴打可以離開冬天地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda885a8f777ac417ab7ea9888d093e8f8cc4b20","tid":42411,"uid":32762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外部設備一定係閂門閂窗<br />\n抽氣扇都一定要熄<br />\n盡量保持沖涼既蒸氣留係入面<br />\n從而保持高溫度<br />\n咁搽身洗頭就無咁凍<br />\n<br />\n利申: 過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抽氣扇沖之前好記得熄 有次唔記得 沖沖下震住咁lan 出浴室門口熄 諗起都慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8a4ff4057e58aabbcdf788db67020f25a45e79","tid":42411,"uid":9375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解要用儲水式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有頭髮邊個想做癩痢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係點解？無煤氣？"}]}